## 1. Which File Is Responsible for Storing Vectors?

**File:** [`backend/services/qdrantService.js`](file:///c:/Users/BAVISHYA/Desktop/lost-and-found/backend/services/qdrantService.js)

| What gets stored | Function | Collection |
|---|---|---|
